    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for Model Risk Level 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 for a Class II device with medium model influence. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions, and the relative hemolysis index predictions satisfy the RH < 1 acceptance criterion across all five evaluated operating points. The credibility evidence package is accepted as sufficient to support the regulatory submission claim.",
